WEBVTT

00:01:20.066 --> 00:01:23.699
mayn nomen iz MIRJAM MARCUS.

00:01:23.699 --> 00:01:28.733
ikh, ha- haynt iz der SIEBZEHNTER merts, nayntsn zeks un NEUNZIG.

00:01:28.733 --> 00:01:32.966
kh'makh a ⟨BEFRAGENUNG⟩ mit, FRAU BASIA Lipis,

00:01:32.966 --> 00:01:36.333
un mir zenen do in Berlin, in DEUTSCHLAND.

00:01:38.418 --> 00:01:41.283
froy Lipis, SAGEN SIE BITTE WIE SIE HEISSEN.

00:01:41.250 --> 00:01:42.693
Basye.

00:01:43.335 --> 00:01:46.299
un vos iz der nomen fun ayer mishpokhe?

00:01:46.628 --> 00:01:48.749
 Lipis.

00:01:48.464 --> 00:01:54.583
kent ir mir zogn mit oytsyes vi men shraybt "BASIA" un vi men shraybt, "Lipis"?

00:01:54.590 --> 00:01:55.346
JA.

00:01:56.213 --> 00:01:57.304
Ba-

00:01:58.221 --> 00:02:01.721
B.A.S.I.A.

00:02:02.082 --> 00:02:04.171
un Lipis, oykhet ⟨mit⟩...?

00:02:03.319 --> 00:02:05.893
Li- L.I.P.

00:02:06.237 --> 00:02:07.446
I.S.

00:02:07.993 --> 00:02:10.946
a dank. ven zent ir geboyrn?

00:02:10.899 --> 00:02:15.428
in toyznt nayn hundert tsvey un draysik, dem tsentn may.

00:02:16.284 --> 00:02:18.497
vi alt zent ir itst?

00:02:18.876 --> 00:02:22.877
ikh veys, fir un zekhtsik ver ikh.

00:02:22.286 --> 00:02:24.416
dakht zikh, tsvey un zekhtsik efsher?

00:02:24.373 --> 00:02:25.856
neyn.

00:02:26.166 --> 00:02:29.130
fir un zekhtsik yor ver ikh dem tsentn may.

00:02:26.217 --> 00:02:27.105
i-...

00:02:28.434 --> 00:02:29.434
UNK.

00:02:29.674 --> 00:02:33.167
vu zent ir geboyrn gevorn, dem nomen fun di shtot?

00:02:33.136 --> 00:02:35.730
geboyrn gevorn in Novoselits.

00:02:36.086 --> 00:02:38.712
kent ir dos zogn oykhet in oytsyes?

00:02:38.907 --> 00:02:40.673
N.O.

00:02:41.151 --> 00:02:42.360
V.

00:02:43.935 --> 00:02:46.072
O.S.

00:02:46.247 --> 00:02:47.523
E.

00:02:47.952 --> 00:02:50.758
L.I.TS.A.

00:02:50.959 --> 00:02:52.022
a dank.

00:02:52.022 --> 00:02:55.032
in velkhn land iz dos, NOWOSELITZA?

00:02:52.206 --> 00:02:53.206
BITTE SCHÖN.

00:02:55.478 --> 00:02:57.176
in Ukraine.

00:02:57.408 --> 00:03:00.534
kent ir dos zogn, ikh bet aykh, oykhet in oytsyes?

00:03:00.275 --> 00:03:02.503
yo. U.K.

00:03:02.503 --> 00:03:06.285
R.A.I.N.A.

00:03:06.154 --> 00:03:07.591
a dank, froy Lipis.

00:03:07.072 --> 00:03:08.326
BITTE SCHÖN.

00:03:08.367 --> 00:03:09.367
froy Lipis,

00:03:09.562 --> 00:03:13.765
kh'vil aykh fregn vegn ayer mishpokhe,

00:03:13.827 --> 00:03:18.520
vegn ayer mishpokhe, vos zent ir geboyrn gevorn in NOWOSELITZA.

00:03:19.103 --> 00:03:22.505
nu, mayn mishpokhe, zogn ver?

00:03:23.659 --> 00:03:24.429
yo.

00:03:25.347 --> 00:03:26.910
 Elye,

00:03:27.338 --> 00:03:29.424
zey hobn gevoynt in Lipkan,

00:03:30.308 --> 00:03:34.014
 Elye, un di mame hot geheysn Rivke.

00:03:34.459 --> 00:03:40.195
nu, lomikh zogn itster az s'iz gev- funem lebn, az, nokh der milkhome hob ikh,

00:03:40.195 --> 00:03:43.566
zikh ervust az, dos iz geven mayn

00:03:45.175 --> 00:03:47.160
bobe mit mayn zeydn.

00:03:47.301 --> 00:03:51.905
ikh hob oysgevaksn ale yorn biz tsu der milkhome un ikh hob nisht gevust

00:03:51.905 --> 00:03:54.849
az dos iz nisht mayn mame, nisht mayn foter.

00:03:54.849 --> 00:03:57.774
un nokh der milkhome, ven ze'mir aheymgekumen,

00:03:57.966 --> 00:04:01.672
hobn mir mayne shvester un brider dertseylt

00:04:01.729 --> 00:04:05.925
az mayn mame iz geshtorbn ven ikh bin alt geven eyn yor,

00:04:06.302 --> 00:04:12.237
un ikh bin geblibn baym zeydn un bay der boben, un ikh fleg zey rufn "mame" un "pape."

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:15.459
un ikh hob nisht gevust ale yorn dos.

00:04:15.786 --> 00:04:22.101
un, nokh der milkhome iz a khaverte mir gebrakht a bild fun mayn eygener mame,

00:04:22.198 --> 00:04:24.993
un dentsmol hob ikh shoyn zikh dervust

00:04:25.067 --> 00:04:30.050
az dos iz geven mayn bobe mit mayn zeydn, nor ikh hob nisht gefilt gornisht,

00:04:30.050 --> 00:04:32.807
vayl zey flegn mikh shtark ophitn.

00:04:33.572 --> 00:04:36.817
ikh hob gevust ⟨az s'iz⟩ a mame mit a foter.

00:04:36.817 --> 00:04:42.200
un in, nokh der milkhome hob ikh mikh derfun dervust. un mayn foter,

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:45.378
efsher lebt er nokh itster, iz in Buenos-Ayres,

00:04:45.486 --> 00:04:47.111
in Argentine.

00:04:47.111 --> 00:04:50.355
er hot mikh gebet- er hot mikh gevolt nemen...

00:04:50.355 --> 00:04:55.689
mayne shvester hobn mir dertseylt... nor mayn bobe hot mikh nisht gegibn.

00:04:56.640 --> 00:05:02.591
zi hot gezogt az got hot tsugenemen a groyse, bin ikh, di kleyne, ir tokhter.

00:05:02.698 --> 00:05:05.932
un azoy bin ikh farblibn UNK zeyer tokhter.

00:05:05.938 --> 00:05:10.117
er hot mir geshribn un nokh der milkhome hot mikh gevolt nemen.

00:05:10.174 --> 00:05:14.296
er hot mir ongeshribn a briv un hot gezogt az er iz gornit shuldik

00:05:14.296 --> 00:05:18.802
vos ikh hob azoy gevaksn, nor helfn hot er mir mit gornisht gekent.

00:05:18.802 --> 00:05:21.018
s'iz geven farmakht ale vegn.

00:05:22.037 --> 00:05:27.669
nu, bin ikh azoy geb-, shoyn nokh der milkhome hob ikh teykef khasene gehat.

00:05:27.669 --> 00:05:31.138
kh'hob gehat a sheyne familye un a voyln man,

00:05:31.138 --> 00:05:32.910
un bin geven tsufridn.

00:05:32.910 --> 00:05:37.421
avade volt ikh nokh gevolt visn tsi lebt er tsi dos, poshet,

00:05:37.917 --> 00:05:42.652
khotsh mi hot er mit mir keyn shum nisht gehat. mi hot gehat mayn bobe

00:05:42.652 --> 00:05:44.048
mit mayn zeydn.

00:05:44.048 --> 00:05:47.119
zey hobn mikh gekhovet, zey hobn mikh gelernt,

00:05:47.119 --> 00:05:53.250
zey hobn mikh ales. un ongetun un opgehit, ales. un di shvester un di brider oykh.

00:05:53.391 --> 00:05:59.884
un ven ze'mir geven in lager, flegn zey ⟨s- sh-⟩ vi m'hot gepakt a shtikl broyt, dos ershte hot men es mir gegibn,

00:05:59.884 --> 00:06:01.602
az ikh zol nisht laydn.

00:06:02.613 --> 00:06:07.957
zog mir, di shvesters un di bruders, vos zenen feters mit mumes, ober ir

00:06:07.957 --> 00:06:11.400
filt zikh vi, tsu zey vi shvesters mit briders,

00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:11.402
 shtark!

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:12.771
zog mir...

00:06:11.402 --> 00:06:14.917
ven mayn shvester, Basye, iz geshtorbn,

00:06:14.974 --> 00:06:19.693
hob ikh gezogt az shoyn! kh'hob shoyn ales farloyrn in lebn.

00:06:21.758 --> 00:06:25.616
 un itster, di, ze'mir geven shtark getray.

00:06:21.825 --> 00:06:22.646
zi iz ge-...

00:06:28.100 --> 00:06:30.341
zi iz geven a shvester, BASIA?

00:06:29.767 --> 00:06:34.242
 mayn mame's shvester, nor zi hot mir gehaltn vi a kind.

00:06:31.393 --> 00:06:32.399
yo.

00:06:34.242 --> 00:06:36.956
zi hot mikh gekhovet, zi hot mir ales.

00:06:37.958 --> 00:06:41.868
nokh der milkhome, ven s'iz geshtorbn der zeyde mit der bobe.

00:06:42.430 --> 00:06:46.693
itster iz do nokh eyn shvester, Zisl. zi iz in Erets-Yisroel.

00:06:42.470 --> 00:06:43.470
i-...

00:06:47.053 --> 00:06:49.831
oykhet hot vegn mir a sakh geton.

00:06:50.698 --> 00:06:54.674
un der bruder itster, eyn, eyner iz geshtorbn,

00:06:54.715 --> 00:07:01.071
 Moyshe, un Srol iz do, nor kh'hob mit im geredt telefon; er veyst shoyn nisht vos er redt.

00:07:01.330 --> 00:07:03.888
er iz shoyn a mentsh ariber di akhtsik.

00:07:04.367 --> 00:07:09.939
er hot mikh geratevet in lager; er fleg loyfn oyf toyt un oyf broyt

00:07:09.939 --> 00:07:13.383
un pakn a bisl vaser un pakn a shtikl broyt oyf di vegn,

00:07:13.383 --> 00:07:15.448
un dos ershte mir tsutrogn,

00:07:15.589 --> 00:07:18.080
az ikh zol nisht blaybn lign.

00:07:18.373 --> 00:07:19.734
nu, ot azoy.

00:07:20.392 --> 00:07:25.770
vos dermant ir zikh fun ayer lebn? ir zent a kleyn kind geven.

00:07:25.770 --> 00:07:30.333
fun dem shtetl NOWOSELITZA vu ir hot gelebt?

00:07:28.830 --> 00:07:32.999
, der zeyd⟨e⟩, letstns hobn gevoynt in

00:07:33.021 --> 00:07:35.900
Lipkan. dos iz Moldavye geven.

00:07:36.143 --> 00:07:41.295
nu, vos ken ikh mikh dermonen? kh'hob gelernt in Tarbus. m'hot mikh gelernt.

00:07:41.295 --> 00:07:42.966
kh'hob gut gelernt.

00:07:42.966 --> 00:07:46.308
un me fleg mikh ontun sheyn, un m'hot mikh opgehit.

00:07:46.308 --> 00:07:51.061
kh'hob gornisht gefilt, tsi s'iz a bobe un a zeyde. ikh hob gemeynt, a mame un a tate.

00:07:51.145 --> 00:07:53.974
un drum, az s'⟨hot gegibn⟩ a ver di milkhome,

00:07:54.486 --> 00:07:59.132
zenen zey dokh nit shuldik geven. zey hobn nisht gevust tsi s'vet azoyns forkumen.

00:07:59.132 --> 00:08:01.688
azoy, s'iz gevorn di milkhome,

00:08:01.688 --> 00:08:04.217
iz ho'mir dokh gevolt antloyfn,

00:08:04.712 --> 00:08:08.910
vayl der elterer bruder hot gezogt az m'vet undz ale oyshargenen.

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:12.615
 zogt er, "l- lomir antloyfn, zikh evakuirn."

00:08:12.615 --> 00:08:16.850
az di froy iz geven in di letste monat, un ho'mir uspeyet biz Britshan.

00:08:16.850 --> 00:08:19.792
dos iz, Moldavye,

00:08:20.322 --> 00:08:23.602
teykef lebn Lipkan un nisht vayt fun Novoselits.

00:08:23.602 --> 00:08:26.326
dortn zenen mir arayngegan tsu mayn,

00:08:26.326 --> 00:08:28.603
heyst es, foter's a khaver,

00:08:28.603 --> 00:08:30.474
un ze'mir dortn geven.

00:08:30.598 --> 00:08:34.653
un s'hot nisht gedoyert keyn sakh. teykef, azoy s'hot zikh ongehoybn ⟨di⟩ milkhome,

00:08:34.653 --> 00:08:38.807
in tsvey vokhn zenen arayngekumen atin, un m'hot ge- ongehoybn makhn

00:08:38.807 --> 00:08:41.172
ash un porekh fun yedn.

00:08:42.931 --> 00:08:46.538
kh'vel, mir veln vayter redn shpeter vegn dem,

00:08:46.351 --> 00:08:47.481
yo.

00:08:46.538 --> 00:08:49.911
ober dokh hob ikh gevolt visn vegn

00:08:49.931 --> 00:08:54.750
di shtot: dos ⟨IST⟩, vi me zogt, a yidish shtetl geven, mit a sakh yidn?

00:08:54.635 --> 00:08:55.407
yo.

00:08:55.407 --> 00:08:59.861
i in Novoselits iz geven a sakh, in Lipkan a sakh, in Britshan.

00:08:59.861 --> 00:09:03.759
ven undz ze'mir shoyn aroy-, ven mir ho'mir uspeyet biz Britshan

00:09:03.759 --> 00:09:06.370
tsu antloyfn, azoy s'hot shoyn ongehoybn shisn,

00:09:06.370 --> 00:09:08.072
oykh geven a sakh yidn.

00:09:08.635 --> 00:09:13.555
un ikh bin geven oyf der shtras; undz ho'mir nisht gevust tsi m'vet azoy shoyn oysshisn

00:09:13.555 --> 00:09:16.267
ven s'zenen arayngekumen di ershte Rumener.

00:09:16.267 --> 00:09:21.329
un azoy zenen arayngekumen, bin ikh geven a kind fun nayn yor, geven mit der elterer shvester

00:09:21.329 --> 00:09:23.414
oyf der hoypt gas, oyf der...

00:09:23.414 --> 00:09:28.870
iz, ⟨ho- ⟩, hobn zey teykef ongehoybn shrayen: oyb s'iz yidn, darf men zey shoyn hargenen,

00:09:28.870 --> 00:09:30.490
vayl s'iz geven a sakh yidn.

00:09:30.490 --> 00:09:33.574
hot zi mikh gekhapt, un ze'mir teykef aheym antlofn,

00:09:33.728 --> 00:09:36.138
in Britshan, bay dem ⟨ot o⟩.

00:09:36.138 --> 00:09:38.109
ze'mir gezesn farmakht,

00:09:38.267 --> 00:09:41.484
un, bay nakht hot shtark geregnt.

00:09:41.642 --> 00:09:45.740
un yidn vos ⟨zey⟩ hobn gevoynt in der glavn⟨e sh-⟩ in der, hoypt shtot,

00:09:45.740 --> 00:09:50.397
 hoyp-, gas, zenen antlofn tsun undz, vayl undz ho'mir gevoynt a bisl vayter.

00:09:50.397 --> 00:09:53.600
un m'hot gezogt az me rabevet un me shist yidn

00:09:53.826 --> 00:09:54.815
shtark.

00:09:54.889 --> 00:09:57.853
zenen zey gezesn, ze'mir gelign ale oyf dr'erd,

00:09:57.876 --> 00:09:59.940
 vayl s'iz nisht geven vu,

00:09:59.940 --> 00:10:02.758
un es hot in droysn shtark geregnt.

00:10:02.758 --> 00:10:05.177
s'iz ibergegan der, di nakht,

00:10:05.267 --> 00:10:10.323
un dem andern tog iz ale di vos hobn gevoynt in der shtot kristn

00:10:10.684 --> 00:10:15.169
hobn zikh teykef genemen rabeven. m'hot gezogt az me meg yidn rabeven.

00:10:15.169 --> 00:10:18.710
iz men arayngekumen. yeder iz gezesn azoy ⟨ot o⟩.

00:10:18.767 --> 00:10:22.088
un zey, vos zey hobn gezen sheyns un guts

00:10:22.088 --> 00:10:23.570
hobn zey gerabevet.

00:10:24.150 --> 00:10:28.413
un der balebos vu undz ze'mir geven hot gehat beheymes,

00:10:28.521 --> 00:10:30.253
finef tsi zeks.

00:10:30.580 --> 00:10:35.361
hot er gehat eynem, azoy a kleynem v- a krist,

00:10:35.361 --> 00:10:38.035
vos er fleg geyn pasen di beheymes.

00:10:38.035 --> 00:10:40.787
azoy er hot zikh dervust az me meg rabeven,

00:10:40.787 --> 00:10:43.166
iz er, a kleyner, ⟨azoy⟩ ⟨UNK⟩o

00:10:43.166 --> 00:10:44.751
arayngekumen

00:10:44.751 --> 00:10:46.814
un iz tsugegan

00:10:46.814 --> 00:10:50.092
aleyn, un hot oyfgemakht do vu di beheymes zenen,

00:10:50.092 --> 00:10:52.805
un zikh aroysgenemen di shenste beheymes,

00:10:52.805 --> 00:10:55.685
un iz avekgegan. der balebos hot ongehoybn shrayen.

00:10:55.685 --> 00:11:00.148
iz, yeder in shtub hot im tsugehaltn, er zol gornisht zogn, vayl host epes gezogt,

00:11:00.148 --> 00:11:02.012
hot men dikh teykef geshosn.

00:11:02.136 --> 00:11:06.289
zenen zey arayngegan; vos m'hot gevolt hobn zey ales tsugenemen.

00:11:06.289 --> 00:11:08.390
un yeder iz gezesn; m'hot geshvign.

00:11:08.852 --> 00:11:12.558
un m'hot shoyn, s'iz durkhgegan tsvey tog, m'hot shoyn nisht gehat vos tsu esn.

00:11:12.868 --> 00:11:16.044
m'hot ales aroysgenemen un gibn hobn zey nisht gevolt.

00:11:16.044 --> 00:11:21.955
zenen gegangen, m'hot gerabevet, me, vos m'hot gezen hot men ales aroysgetrogn fun di shtiber.

00:11:21.918 --> 00:11:25.992
dos zenen di kristn, di shkheynim, di shkheynim geven?

00:11:23.896 --> 00:11:25.985
di kristn vos zey hobn gevo-

00:11:25.985 --> 00:11:28.167
DA. yo, yo, yo, yo.

00:11:27.724 --> 00:11:29.839
ver iz geven mit aykh,

00:11:30.416 --> 00:11:32.246
fun ayer mishpokhe?

00:11:31.802 --> 00:11:33.503
ale ze'mir geven dort.

00:11:32.909 --> 00:11:33.666
UNK.

00:11:33.503 --> 00:11:34.284
ale.

00:11:34.284 --> 00:11:37.365
un der bruder mit der froy, mit der shvanger froy,

00:11:37.365 --> 00:11:40.058
un der bru- un der, froy's,

00:11:40.058 --> 00:11:44.262
muter mitn foter. a f- a fule shtub mit mentshn geven.

00:11:44.262 --> 00:11:47.644
dem andern tog hot men zikh genemen shlepn yidishe meydlekh.

00:11:47.644 --> 00:11:49.818
m'hot oysgekloybn di shenste

00:11:49.818 --> 00:11:52.175
un m'hot genemen, m'hot gemakht fun zey khoyzek.

00:11:52.175 --> 00:11:55.412
iz, azoy ze'mir geven a fule shtub mit mentshn,

00:11:55.412 --> 00:11:59.201
iz arayngekumen tsun undz, gedenk ikh, eyner a Rumener,

00:11:59.292 --> 00:12:00.824
a,

00:12:00.824 --> 00:12:05.701
un iz arayngekumen. un mayn shvester, di vos zi iz itster in, Erets-Yisroel,

00:12:05.701 --> 00:12:09.236
iz yeder gezesn, iz er tsugegan un hot zi oysgekloybn.

00:12:09.236 --> 00:12:13.024
zi iz geven a meydl fun akhtsn, nayntsn yor.

00:12:13.024 --> 00:12:15.755
un hot zi oysgekloybn, hot gezogt, "kum mit mir."

00:12:16.217 --> 00:12:20.390
iz mayn mame, s'heyst di bobe, az zi hot dos derzen...

00:12:20.390 --> 00:12:24.574
un ikh bin geshtanen, kh'hob zikh tsugehaltn bay ir, bay, lebn der boben.

00:12:24.574 --> 00:12:26.702
ikh hob geveynt, vos kh'hob moyre gehat...

00:12:26.702 --> 00:12:28.549
hot zi gegibn a zog,

00:12:28.549 --> 00:12:31.574
un er hot zi shoyn gehaltn bay der hant, er zol zi nemen.

00:12:31.574 --> 00:12:36.039
hot zi genemen un hot gezogt, un iz aroys fornt, far ir,

00:12:36.130 --> 00:12:38.793
un hot gezogt, "oyb du nemst zi,

00:12:38.793 --> 00:12:40.224
nem mikh oykhet,

00:12:40.399 --> 00:12:42.063
un nem undz ale."

00:12:42.222 --> 00:12:44.504
un, un hot zikh genemen veynen

00:12:44.504 --> 00:12:47.504
un im kushn di fis, er zol zi nisht tshepen.

00:12:47.504 --> 00:12:50.241
un ikh bin oykh geshtanen lebn ir. ikh hob geveynt.

00:12:50.241 --> 00:12:55.213
un azoy zi hot zikh gegibn a loz tsu geyn, iz ale mentshn vos iz geven in shtub,

00:12:55.213 --> 00:12:59.405
nu, di zin un m⟨i⟩t ale, hobn zikh gegibn a loz lebn ir nokh,

00:12:59.405 --> 00:13:04.510
un m'iz nokhgegan mit ir. iz er geblibn shteyn oyf der tir. er hot gezen, s'iz tsu fil mentshn,

00:13:04.510 --> 00:13:08.478
un m'hot im shtark gebetn. hot er gegibn a makh mit der hant un iz avek.

00:13:08.344 --> 00:13:09.478
dos i-...

