00:23:59.139 --> 00:24:03.468
dos heyst, es hot shoyn geendikt zikh, zumer?.

00:24:00.595 --> 00:24:05.632
 osyen. der zumer. nu, di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn ⟨dem⟩ tsvey un tsvontsikstn ⟨yuni⟩.

00:24:04.557 --> 00:24:09.366
un ir zent nokh geven mit ayer, mit der mamen, mit dem zeydn?

00:24:07.139 --> 00:24:12.227
y- ale ze'mir geven. oyfn besoylem hot men undz fart-...

00:24:09.392 --> 00:24:11.772
zey hobn aykh opgehitn?

00:24:12.227 --> 00:24:14.043
vos hot men gekent ophitn?

00:24:14.043 --> 00:24:16.455
esn hot keyner dir nisht gegibn,

00:24:16.455 --> 00:24:19.126
un vaser hot men dikh nisht gelozt nemen.

00:24:19.126 --> 00:24:23.468
mayn, der vos er lebt nokh in IZRAIL' iz geven azoy a,

00:24:23.468 --> 00:24:26.392
a sh-, mentsh vos er iz gelofn, gefloygn.

00:24:26.392 --> 00:24:30.746
fleg er aroysloyfn di ershte, ven s'flegn eynike mentshn gute

00:24:30.746 --> 00:24:34.873
aroyskumen gibn a shtikl broyt, gibn a kap vaser. fleg er khapn

00:24:34.873 --> 00:24:36.638
un dos ershte mir trogn.

00:24:36.638 --> 00:24:38.835
dortn ze'mir gezesn bay der,

00:24:38.835 --> 00:24:42.038
ven m'- m'iz geshtanen un m'hot gevart, me zol oysshisn,

00:24:42.038 --> 00:24:45.411
bin ikh geven in gantsn fardart di lipn,

00:24:45.417 --> 00:24:50.265
un kh'ho- bin geshtanen un ikh hob geveynt. kh'hob nisht gehat keyn vaser, nisht esn.

00:24:50.265 --> 00:24:57.151
iz er gekumen un ⟨hot azoy ot o mir⟩, di lipn a bisl gemakht. yeder hot geesn roye kartoflyes,

00:24:57.151 --> 00:25:01.731
roye burikes, ver s'hot gegibn, fun der erd dortn ven m'iz gegan, aroysgenemen.

00:25:01.731 --> 00:25:05.164
ikh hob dos nisht gekent esn. iz gegangen

00:25:05.164 --> 00:25:08.523
⟨e-⟩ der, der ⟨ge-⟩, Srol,

00:25:08.523 --> 00:25:12.798
der bruder, un hot, iz gegan un hot gezen a beyml mit grine flomen.

00:25:12.906 --> 00:25:18.329
hot er opgerisn etlekhe flomen; er hot mitn lebn, rizikirt,

00:25:18.329 --> 00:25:20.544
un hot mir gebrakht di flomen.

00:25:20.544 --> 00:25:25.095
iz a flom hob ikh gegesn. gedenk ikh biz hayntikn tog az ikh bin shoyn geven far-

00:25:25.095 --> 00:25:27.044
farshmakht strashne,

00:25:27.044 --> 00:25:30.332
nor a flom hob ikh genemen un ikh hob durkhgekayet.

00:25:30.338 --> 00:25:35.833
un, zi, di mame iz geshtanen lebn mir, ⟨iz zi⟩ geven gliklekh az ikh kaye shoyn epes.

00:25:37.054 --> 00:25:41.773
 un dentsmol ven ⟨undz ho'⟩mir shoyn, getrofn oyf dem besoylem,

00:25:42.353 --> 00:25:45.637
hob ikh gehat tsvey groyse shvartse tsep.

00:25:45.897 --> 00:25:54.651
iz dos, hob ikh shtark, gedenk ikh derfar vos, d- az oyf dem besoylem iz dos forgekumen. az zey hobn gezen umreyne,

00:25:54.651 --> 00:25:59.728
nokh in lager in Sukeran, flegn zey teykef shisn; zey hobn moyre gehat far epidemyes.

00:26:00.021 --> 00:26:03.966
un ikh bin gegan mit di tsep. kemen hot men mikh nisht gekemt,

00:26:03.966 --> 00:26:07.027
gornisht. ikh bin geven farflokhtn mit lentes,

00:26:07.027 --> 00:26:08.192
mit ban⟨dn⟩.

00:26:08.340 --> 00:26:18.948
ikh gey un halt mikh in eyn kratsn un kratsn. zey hobn, a klal, di eltere shvester hot gegibn a derze, ikh halt mikh in eyn kratsn, un heybt oyf di tsep: ful.

00:26:19.427 --> 00:26:25.867
vos zol men tun? zi hot nokh moyre tsu zogn, me zol, nu, vayl m'hot moyre gehat far epidemyes. a klal, zi zogt...

00:26:25.873 --> 00:26:29.531
di mame hot nisht gezen azoy gut; zi iz shoyn geven in di yorn.

00:26:29.531 --> 00:26:32.366
zogt zi, "vos zoln mir tun? vos zoln mir tun?" iker,

00:26:32.366 --> 00:26:36.903
di brider hobn ongehoybn tsu loyfn. mit vos zol men nemen? ⟨epes hot men⟩ getrofn a hekl.

00:26:36.943 --> 00:26:42.956
hot men gevolt mitn hekl mir hakn di tsep, un, ⟨⟩, hor iz shver ⟨iz⟩ dokh optsushnaydn.

00:26:42.956 --> 00:26:45.391
un ikh zits un veyn!

00:26:45.391 --> 00:26:49.869
un m'hot mikh anidergeleygt UNK dos zol keyner nisht zen, ⟨un⟩ me vil hakn mit dem hekl,

00:26:49.869 --> 00:26:51.331
un m'hot nisht gekent.

00:26:51.405 --> 00:26:54.892
iker, iz di, ⟨ot o⟩ eltere,

00:26:55.438 --> 00:27:04.240
 Basye, di shvester, az zi hot dos derzen hot zi shtark geveynt un hot ongehoybn loyfn tsevishn mentshn. m'hot ir gezogt az s'iz do a frizerke ergets.

00:27:04.416 --> 00:27:08.522
iz zi tsugegan tsun ir, un zi hot zi gekent, un hot ir ongehoybn zogn

00:27:08.522 --> 00:27:13.087
vos s'iz geshen. ⟨iz zi⟩ gekumen tsu loyfn mit a sherl.

00:27:13.090 --> 00:27:19.111
⟨un⟩ azoy zenen geven farflokhtn biz aroyf, azoy hot men zey mir opgeshoyrn un m'hot zey gegibn a leyg anider.

00:27:19.111 --> 00:27:20.907
gedenk ikh az der,

00:27:21.100 --> 00:27:24.443
vos er iz shoyn geshtorbn, der bruder, hot azoy geveynt,

00:27:24.443 --> 00:27:28.898
az ikh gedenk nit a MUZHCHINA zol azoy veynen, a man,

00:27:28.898 --> 00:27:32.412
azoy er hot geveynt ven er hot derzen di tsep azoy ⟨ot o⟩ lign.

00:27:32.412 --> 00:27:34.214
un hot genemen di tsep,

00:27:34.214 --> 00:27:39.862
un m'hot zey nokh ergets fartrogn, s'zol keyner nisht zen. derfar gedenk ikh shtark gut in,

00:27:39.862 --> 00:27:44.618
in Molev dem besoylem. dortn hobn mir zikh opgevalgert etlekhe gute teg,

00:27:44.618 --> 00:27:48.153
un drum hot men ergets in Molev undz arayngetribn in a,

00:27:48.153 --> 00:27:52.632
in di, vu me fleg haltn kuen mit beheymes.

00:27:52.632 --> 00:27:58.674
hot men undz arayngetribn. ze'mir geven etlekhe tog, nor m'hot dokh gedarft gibn esn, m'hot dokh gedarft epes, mentshn fil.

00:27:58.674 --> 00:28:02.036
un drum hobn zey gereshet, me zol vayter ongeyn.

00:28:02.652 --> 00:28:07.483
un m'hot undz getribn fun dorf tsu dorf, fun dorf tsu dorf,

00:28:07.483 --> 00:28:12.018
un nisht esn un nisht trinken. ver s'iz oyf di vegn anidergefaln.

00:28:12.018 --> 00:28:14.069
trupn hostu gezen fil.

00:28:15.949 --> 00:28:23.201
un, un, un ⟨b-⟩ m'hot undz azoy lang getribn biz s'iz shoyn arayn in tifn osyen.

00:28:23.404 --> 00:28:25.009
ven nokh,

00:28:25.028 --> 00:28:28.284
kh'vil aykh nokh fregn, vos es iz geven

00:28:28.302 --> 00:28:31.128
in di lagers, in di,

00:28:31.128 --> 00:28:33.577
Molev hot ir gezogt a nomen?

00:28:32.559 --> 00:28:38.879
Molev, MOGILЁV, etlekhe, a, ikh gedenk nisht vifl; dort vintsik ze'mir geven.

00:28:38.879 --> 00:28:41.064
m'hot undz teykef vayter getribn.

00:28:41.064 --> 00:28:44.799
s'i- vayzt oys, zey hobn getribn ammeystn me zol dergeyn,

00:28:45.816 --> 00:28:48.871
derfar vos, m'hot dentsmol gezogt un,

00:28:48.871 --> 00:28:53.456
 hob ikh gehert, un dernokh dem hobn mentshn gezogt azoy, m'hot azoy shtark geshosn,

00:28:53.479 --> 00:28:58.495
iz, hobn zey gezogt, me zol oyfhern shisn. me zol poshet zamutshen mentshn.

00:28:58.495 --> 00:29:01.421
zey hobn nisht gehat mit di trupn vu tsu ahintsutun.

00:29:01.630 --> 00:29:05.204
iz, f- ze'mir in Molev a bisl geven,

00:29:05.204 --> 00:29:06.992
un m'hot undz v⟨ay⟩ter getribn.

00:29:07.060 --> 00:29:08.541
yo. fun dem ver-...
